### Get All Currencies
GET http://localhost:8081/v1/api/currencies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get All Currencies with Query Parameters
GET http://localhost:8081/v1/api/currencies?filter=example&page=0&size=10&sort=currencyId,asc
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get Currency by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/v1/api/currencies/10000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Create Currency
POST http://localhost:8081/v1/api/currencies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "currencyCode": "USD",
  "currencyName": "US Dollar",
  "isActive": true
}

### Update Currency
PUT http://localhost:8081/v1/api/currencies/10000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "currencyCode": "EUR",
  "currencyName": "Euro",
  "isActive": false
}

### Delete Currency
DELETE http://localhost:8081/v1/api/currencies/10001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>
